Context: The Automation Technician Certificate program is a self-paced Distance Education program offered by George Brown College. It is designed for adult learners seeking independent study in the field of manufacturing technology. The program has no post-secondary academic prerequisites and is open to anyone who wishes to obtain their Automation Technician certificate.
